Kyrgios was slapped with a $16500 penalty for his meltdown at the Shanghai Masters, where he tanked points, swore and argued with fans before being booed off court.It follows a catalogue of similar incidents for the talented but troubled 21-year-old, whose rise to world No14 has been punctuated by controversy."I couldn't care less, to be completely honest with you," Kyrgios said. "Just - big deal." - AFP